                                <li title="Comentario Bíblico de 1 Samuel 16"><a href="../../comentario-biblico/?v=BL95&amp;co=matthew-henry&amp;l=1+samuel&amp;cap=16" target="_blank"><span class="icon-book"></span></a></li>
